                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The subjects depicted within the living mural all reach out at once to attack. The living mural makes a fist Strike against each target within range.</p>\n<p>These attacks count toward the living mural's multiple attack penalty, but this penalty doesn't increase until after all of the attacks are made.</p>"
